title: Brittany Drake from Pity Sex
itunes:title: Brittany Drake from Pity Sex
description:
One of my favorite discussions is on this episode with Brittany Drake from Pity Sex where we speak about psychology, being a female in independent music and being positive. It's a very enlightening chat and showcases how you can have interests outside of the art that you create. Please visit my fundraising page to help the show: http://www.patreon.com/xpurposex
